{"ts":"2026-07-07T06:49:24.311Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Repro: 'pm context --json --max-items 5' -> unknown_option; examples only suggest pm context --help.\n\nWhy it matters: project management = context management — agents reason in 'max items / top N' terms when bounding token spend, and every failed guess costs a help round-trip. This is the same recovery-hint class as GH-458 (pm-qfte, shipped: lifecycle --assignee alias) and generalizes under pm-gdi7 (unknown-option errors should suggest valid flags). If pm-gdi7's generalized did-you-mean suggestion engine lands first, this item reduces to a targeted test case plus the alias decision.\n\nDuplicate-check evidence: pm search 'GH-476' -> 0 hits; pm search 'context row limit aliases' -> no open coverage; pm-gdi7 covers the generic suggestion engine but not this specific alias/hint."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-5h9g"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-476: pm context rejects --max-items with an untargeted unknown_option (alias or recovery hint)"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Fleet dogfood (GH-476): an agent naturally tried 'pm context --max-items 5' to bound token usage; pm rejects it with a generic unknown_option and no pointer to the supported --limit flag, forcing an extra help round-trip."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Task"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":2},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-ux","area:cli","gh-issue"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-07T06:49:24.311Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-07T06:49:24.311Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":60},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Either --max-items is accepted as a hidden alias for --limit on pm context (contracts/completions/docs wired per the new-flag checklist), or the unknown_option error for --max-items returns a targeted hint naming 'pm context --limit <n>'; regression test covers the chosen behavior; GH-476 closed with shipped evidence"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-mpbb"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/dependencies","value":[{"id":"pm-gdi7","kind":"related","created_at":"2026-07-07T06:49:24.311Z"}]}],"before_hash":"3cc22dff72be7b14824654a7a64ea62b04799939b2fee54c1b5f52ca60bf6df0","after_hash":"d8930f0ef217e5f5faf59c5f1cc62964cbdbb57b1ec8eedc797c3e62e2f6eaa8","message":""}
